==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Coating
<hw>Coat"ing</hw> <pr>(k⟦omac⟧"⟦icr⟧ng)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>A coat or covering; a layer of any substance, as a cover or
protection; <as>as, the <ex>coating</ex> of a retort or
vial</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Cloth for coats; <as>as, an assortment of
<ex>coatings</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Coatless</ent>⟦br⟧
